@CurrencyRates.GatewayService.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Health
GET {{CurrencyRates.GatewayService.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Dev token via gateway (proxied to Finance, anonymous)
# @name getToken
POST {{CurrencyRates.GatewayService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/finance/dev/token
Accept: application/json

###

### User rates via gateway (JWT required)
GET {{CurrencyRates.GatewayService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/finance/rates
Authorization: Bearer {{getToken.response.body.$.token}}
Accept: application/json

###
